Mister...

16
00:00:53,163 --> 00:00:55,847
My mom will be okay, right?

17
00:00:55,847 --> 00:00:58,314
It's not serious, is it?

18
00:01:03,053 --> 00:01:06,500
I only said awful things to her...

19
00:01:07,161 --> 00:01:10,230
What if something happens to her?

20
00:01:11,816 --> 00:01:14,724
I told her I didn't want to live with her anymore.

21
00:01:14,724 --> 00:01:18,344
But I didn't mean it. I need to tell her that...

22
00:01:19,293 --> 00:01:22,591
What if she just leaves me?

23
00:01:27,349 --> 00:01:29,322
Life and death are in the hands of the heavens.

24
00:01:29,322 --> 00:01:33,465
No amount of worry can change fate...

25
00:01:35,288 --> 00:01:37,705
So let us wait patiently.

26
00:01:44,454 --> 00:01:46,523
Excuse me.

27
